{"tid":2515512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"高登創辦人 DrJim：回憶都是美好的，高登文化要傳承下去","createTime":"2021-05-04T04:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T11:48:18.000Z","uid":1886,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ae8c974b06b9273b236ea25774f61fddf3be7233","tid":2515512,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:56:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://drjimdiary.blogspot.com/2017/09/blog-post.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdrjimdiary.blogspot.com%2F2017%2F09%2Fblog-post.html&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=41d5b3e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://drjimdiary.blogspot.com/2017/09/blog-post.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"violet\">DrJim<br />\n1999年創辦香港高登，於2008年正式賣盤。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔知佢今時今日見到高登搞到就快要執有咩感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149afaec6f7615b97db94801b36d96208b82fd16","tid":2515512,"uid":1886,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:57:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"violet\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>歲月神偷 - 高登開站文獻</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n上個月其中一位高登的舊拍檔陳先生搵我，告訴我他的 Office 要搬了，問我一些封塵已久的高登舊的文件還要不要保留。我說不如先給我看一下吧，其中一些文件可能有紀念價值。<br />\n<br />\n翻開這此舊文件，都已經是15、16年前的往事了。回憶都是美好的，但是也沒必要老是把舊東西儲下來，所以最後決定把文件丟掉前拍了一些照片給大家分享：<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-lwoDJN3TlEw/Wa6ky3YLX4I/AAAAAAAAAcM/xlGnmXodWRM1WLs0Hhn6GsIdaa4E7-fMwCLcBGAs/s640/IMG_5044.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-lwoDJN3TlEw%2FWa6ky3YLX4I%2FAAAAAAAAAcM%2FxlGnmXodWRM1WLs0Hhn6GsIdaa4E7-fMwCLcBGAs%2Fs640%2FIMG_5044.JPG&h=df7f2c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-STt3n6xvieo/Wa6ky6j_nUI/AAAAAAAAAcQ/oOdOFZZZ2mQe0ZbpLJA_D2C7PelUAIWkQCLcBGAs/s640/IMG_5045.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-STt3n6xvieo%2FWa6ky6j_nUI%2FAAAAAAAAAcQ%2FoOdOFZZZ2mQe0ZbpLJA_D2C7PelUAIWkQCLcBGAs%2Fs640%2FIMG_5045.JPG&h=cee59109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這兩份銀行月結單，見證了當時高登會員的熱誠和支持。當時網上銀行和電子支付還未流行，但是每天都有不少網友願意花$38/88通過ATM過數給我們做高級會員。感激！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3KjG2JPd9vk/Wa6kzo5CeiI/AAAAAAAAAcY/4VfBbhQWLV80O61qeaCpkn1unYVFvH4bACLcBGAs/s640/IMG_5047.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-3KjG2JPd9vk%2FWa6kzo5CeiI%2FAAAAAAAAAcY%2F4VfBbhQWLV80O61qeaCpkn1unYVFvH4bACLcBGAs%2Fs640%2FIMG_5047.JPG&h=df971927&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時PIII 1G PC要萬幾元一部<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-6Dq2KrstPpo/Wa6kz1N__LI/AAAAAAAAAcc/ag4Dj0sbZY0JvdP5KbHtlaG9N0RpY3gAwCLcBGAs/s640/IMG_5048.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-6Dq2KrstPpo%2FWa6kz1N__LI%2FAAAAAAAAAcc%2Fag4Dj0sbZY0JvdP5KbHtlaG9N0RpY3gAwCLcBGAs%2Fs640%2FIMG_5048.JPG&h=393448f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時的版面設計和「膳稿」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Gq49jmqnbp8/Wa6kz4Wmt3I/AAAAAAAAAcg/RvnVTsLUya4-gEbiLxTVYPXxw66IyqfqgCLcBGAs/s640/IMG_5049.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Gq49jmqnbp8%2FWa6kz4Wmt3I%2FAAAAAAAAAcg%2FRvnVTsLUya4-gEbiLxTVYPXxw66IyqfqgCLcBGAs%2Fs640%2FIMG_5049.JPG&h=79188d22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開站時的宣傳稿，當時每日瀏覽人數有1,000人 :-) 現在有 1,000萬了吧!?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-CsWVp-d81Fg/Wa6k0aW7y9I/AAAAAAAAAck/pGt23zjhuO8cdq6B0WDXTw0GUiEkh21EgCLcBGAs/s640/IMG_5052.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-CsWVp-d81Fg%2FWa6k0aW7y9I%2FAAAAAAAAAck%2FpGt23zjhuO8cdq6B0WDXTw0GUiEkh21EgCLcBGAs%2Fs640%2FIMG_5052.JPG&h=a698bb5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾幾何時，我們也曾經賣過音效卡和小喇叭，最後當然是失敗告終<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-i4x2TU3khz0/Wa6rqtk08wI/AAAAAAAAAc4/BdO3oYvd_uIdiT7khDesEJcoZQ7Udx77QCLcBGAs/s640/post_asp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-i4x2TU3khz0%2FWa6rqtk08wI%2FAAAAAAAAAc4%2FBdO3oYvd_uIdiT7khDesEJcoZQ7Udx77QCLcBGAs%2Fs640%2Fpost_asp.png&h=94aaaa43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部份ASP原碼<br />\n<br />\n當時成立高登除了為興趣外，有兩個主要目標：<br />\n1) 不要虧本 ; <br />\n2) 高登文化要存承下去。<br />\n<br />\n今天回顧，兩個目標均已經達到。而上面的文件，當是歷史的一部份吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1390000/1391644/sksinn20151202401_1_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1390000%2F1391644%2Fsksinn20151202401_1_1024.JPG&h=cba37933&s={SIZE}\" /></p>"},{"pid":"495494f420b358512ab7305477eabd2c4ee7a7bb","tid":2515512,"uid":36014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c4f467a8d70277e0bb6351e7b9c1adf0f15b73","tid":2515512,"uid":138197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:01:58.000Z","msg":"印度佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457ad8ec00406ae99b78e0362cb4de0a4ac52198","tid":2515512,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:03:28.000Z","msg":"DrJim（高登會員編號：21701），原名王國良，大家稱為「高登之父」，是香港高登創辦人之一，曾在2000年至2003年中擔任高登討論區管理員。他當年在網上隨便選了一名印度人半身照，作為他的頭像。他成功將香港高登由一個提供電腦硬件行情的網站，演變成為受香港網民歡迎的討論區品牌，深受高登會員愛戴。"},{"pid":"3fb3c39c1570e433235d864079b803eaf0ef4375","tid":2515512,"uid":39710,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:03:38.000Z","msg":"果陣已經一地都係app都仲唔肯搞已經衰<br />\n<br />\n仲要分八個ser 八個網址<br />\n<br />\n加埋以前啲濕鳩嘢, 垃圾admin同iProA單嘢<br />\n<br />\n多種功能衰竭死亡，懷緬下就算"},{"pid":"e8f80016d506c64684204708b8173b3676b9d041","tid":2515512,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:03:48.000Z","msg":"約1999年，因科網熱潮興起，當時在銀行從事資訊科技工作的 DrJim 工作比較穩定，於是在2000年創立「香港高登」網站，概念源自深水埗高登電腦商場。網站除列出各樣電腦產品的價格外，亦有「占博士」專頁及討論區，分別刊登由 DrJim 撰寫的電腦硬件測試報告，及當時網民的電腦軟硬件討論。隨着香港高登網站越來越有名，他在討論區開設「吹水台」，讓網民談論與電腦無關的話題。"},{"pid":"7d1876b45e05f060177127b8915b7ffd4d1e3ded","tid":2515512,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"在2003年初，他因工作理由將香港高登賣給資訊科技暨教學公司「科域盈創」（Fevaworks），並辭去管理員一職。"},{"pid":"3ad0afaaffa21ebb149c6e575744582efb072556","tid":2515512,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fb3c39c1570e433235d864079b803eaf0ef4375","tid":2515512,"uid":39710,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:03:38.000Z","msg":"果陣已經一地都係app都仲唔肯搞已經衰<br />\n<br />\n仲要分八個ser 八個網址<br />\n<br />\n加埋以前啲濕鳩嘢, 垃圾admin同iProA單嘢<br />\n<br />\n多種功能衰竭死亡，懷緬下就算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8210b4fa81177221ceadcd71a3cf4c7c895ddfa","tid":2515512,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:05:51.000Z","msg":"DrJim: 有朋友最近問我對高登和 LIHKG 事件有什麼睇法，我的答案是...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/54544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/54544</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"666dc6e3692191d6b95d1a8d07fa5f8119152b37","tid":2515512,"uid":264121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f00a0d5dea97e97c01f6db817444d27dc4e4bc8","tid":2515512,"uid":248299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:07:40.000Z","msg":"haha, bullshit."},{"pid":"946d63fe92120ee3037621fdb72a32b7ed9c0ff7","tid":2515512,"uid":285415,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"聽講佢而家做某銀